name: Quantum Quokka Inc.
philosophy: Where Reality Melts and Imagination Bakes
features: **Chaos-Engine Navigation:** Say goodbye to boring menus! Our site navigates based on your mood and internet browsing history, surprising you with unexpected connections and content.
**Dream Weaver Integration:**Upload a dream and we'll visually transform it into a unique page, complete with interactive elements based on your subconscious desires.

**Quantum Quokka Biofeedback:**Our AI analyzes your biofeedback data (heart rate, brainwaves) and adjusts the website's layout and colour palette in real-time, creating a personalized sensory experience.

hero.headline: Welcome to the Quantum Quokka Circus!  Step right up and lose yourself in the absurd.
